# 9) How does cloning a repository differ from pulling from a repository?
    # cloning a repository is when you take a repository from GitHub and put it onto your computer (it was not there beforehand). Pulling from a repository is when you make changes/updates to it (The example used in lecture was downloading a game is like cloning a repositiory and any future updates you make to that game are similar to pulling from a repository.).
